{
  "stem": "24462.3",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I knew that the curfew is eight o'clock or something like this.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So I asked the man who was sitting next to me-- I told him a story about I am just coming from the Ukraine.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I was caught, whatever the story was.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I can't remember.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Anyway, tell me if you have somebody where I can stay a few days until I find my work, my family, my everything.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And he gave me an address.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He gave me an address, a couple, older couple, who's son was working in the embassy, the Polish embassy, in London.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "What he did, I don't know, this vice-consul or something.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It wasn't the ambassador.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he said they were very helpful people.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The names, I can't remember anymore.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And tell them that I sent you.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And my name is Kowalski.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Now, Kowalski is John Smith.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And can you imagine who is John Smith?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So anyway, I found the address.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I went.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It was dark.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I knocked on the door.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They didn't want to open.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I spoke through the-- Mr.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Kowalski sent me.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "What Kowalski?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "What Kowalski?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "We don't let-- but still, he opened the door.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Once he opened the door, I put my foot as [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Because it was desperate.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not to get into the, too the house, into the flat, it was death.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They will catch you in a minute.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the, the winter was cold, minus 15, minus-- 20.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Not terrible, but minus 20 at night is unpleasant.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Once he opened this, I started talking nicely Polish.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And then, oh, no I can't-- but maybe you can sleep in the kitchen on the table, on the table in the kitchen.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So I came in.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
